## Factor Investment Analysis (Python)

This project explores the performance of three key equity investment factors:

- Small Cap
- Momentum
- Value

### 🎯 Purpose
The goal of this analysis is to evaluate how different equity factors behave over time
and how they compare to a broad market benchmark.

### 🔍 Approach
- Historical performance analysis of each factor
- Benchmark comparison using MSCI World
- Focus on risk-adjusted performance rather than pure returns

### 📊 Metrics
- Annualized return
- Volatility
- Sharpe ratio
- Correlation between factors

### ➕ Extra
The analysis also evaluates potential diversification benefits and improvements in
risk-adjusted returns when combining the factors into a mixed portfolio.

⚠️ This project does not provide any investment advice
